{
  "title": "EQBSL Explorer — Interactive Evidence-Based Subjective Logic Platform",
  "description": "Interactive web application for the EQBSL (Evidence-based Quantum-resistant Belief State Logic) framework — a mathematically rigorous replacement for scalar trust scores. Models the full epistemic state using evidence tuples (positive, negative, uncertainty, quality) and supports zero-knowledge trust verification and quantum-resistant extensions.\n\nImplements: EQBSL (DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.19056322), CATHEXIS trust-handle layer (DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.19083966), Shadowgraph HD social graph (DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.19056324), and Plenum collective field architecture (DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.19080708).",
